folder: Wyckoff Avenue & Summerfield Avenue, Queens, NY
text:
Wyckoff Ave., north side, west from Summerfield Ave., showing the Slocum House (third from corner; mansard roof; with dormer windows). This house formerly stood on the south side of Wyckoff Ave. in ground belonging to the Malt Diastase Company, located at the S.W. corner of Wyckoff and Decatur Street.

Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.

January 1924.
